General.Name: Dynamic Medical Technologies
General.Description: Dynamic Medical Technologies Inc. maintains, markets, and sells aesthetic lasers and light-based equipment in Taiwan. The company distributes aesthetic medical devices, body contouring devices, dermal fillers, and cosmeceuticals. It also offers aesthetician training and clinical operation consultation services. Dynamic Medical Technologies Inc. was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
